=610 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the default mission based mode, completing objectives while struggling to survive. Or try the Gauntlet mode, where your stage progress is saved and the difficulty scales endlessly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/cbcc33fc3baac199afe4f993a2b15923.poster.avif?t=1762586622\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/cbcc33fc3baac199afe4f993a2b15923.webm?t=1762586622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/cbcc33fc3baac199afe4f993a2b15923.mp4?t=1762586622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/acf91aa5ebab0658d51e46bfb4ec6f2a.webp?t=1762586622\" width=616 height=8 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-4 players (up to 8 supported unofficially)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated maps and objectives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free-form combat: maintain control of your movement while always having access to your sword and firearm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loadouts: Equip weapons, add mods to them and choose paths to create your own class</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-run progression: rogue-lite style upgrades for both you and your enemies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meta-progression: Unlock and upgrade gear between missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 game-modes: Multi-Act primary mode, a smaller standard mission mode and an endless difficulty climber</p></li></ul><p clas